NUMBER 1203
NAME Cavern, Passage
DARKNESS
CAVE
REGION 15
CALL 33
*DESCRIPTION_START
The smooth passages continue until you come to a large cavern with stalactites and stalagmites looming ominously in a rough circle at the far end. There are a few pieces of broken stalactites here and there.
*DESCRIPTION_END
ITEM 0 363
ITEM 1 368
EXIT NW 1200

IFPREVERB SEARCH -1
  VARIABLE SEARCHCAVE
  RANDOM SEARCHCAVE 1 100 0
   IFVAR SEARCHCAVE < 25
    NEWITEM 2 63 VAL2=1205
    ECHO PLAYER You have found a hidden crevice between the stalactites and stalagmites!
    ECHO OTHERS %N seems to have found something near the back wall.
   ELSE
    ECHO PLAYER You find nothing of interest.
    EQUAL ROUNDTIME 3
   ENDIF
ENDIF

IFPREVERB GO 2
  VARIABLE DROPSTAL
  RANDOM DROPSTAL 1 100 0
   IFVAR DROPSTAL < 15
     DAMAGEPLR CRUSH 150 As you slip into the crevice a huge stalactite falls from the ceiling and brushes your body.
    ELSE
     ECHO PLAYER You slip through the crevice without touching a stalagmite on the ground.
     ECHO OTHERS %N slips silently through the crevice.
   ENDIF
ENDIF

